                and uncompromising quality.
                <br /><br />
                Each piece in our collection is a testament to meticulous craftsmanship,
                utilizing only the finest materials to ensure a perfect blend of style and
                durability.
            </p>
            <a href="#" style="color:var(--gold); font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-decoration:none;">LEARN MORE →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
            <img src="images/blackheelverthree.png" alt="About Us" class="flipped-image" style="width:100%;" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="contact-area-section">
    <div class="contact-text-content">
        <h2>CONTACT US</h2>
        <p style="font-size:18px; opacity:0.8; line-height:1.8; color:white;">
